THEY allegedly caught him red-handed stealing! Instead of brutally beating him, they forced him to eat a live chicken. A video has emerged on social media showing the man eating a live chicken as a punishment. In the footage, the alleged thug is seen sitting on the floor while he is forced to eat the chicken. It is not clear where and when was the video was taken. According to a Ghana news publication, GhBase, the man is believed to be in his late thirties. “He was subjected to inhumane act after he was caught red-handed stealing. “He was reportedly caught stealing and instead of the mob lynching him, they ordered him to eat the live chicken that he was caught stealing,” the article read.